  "name": "Guiding Spirit",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/sundries/books/book-embossed-jewel-gold-purple.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl47_LabelType\">Few understand the medium&rsquo;s willingness to harbor powerful spirits, but even if you aren&rsquo;t one of these talented few, you&rsquo;ve always identified with their abilities. You&rsquo;ve always felt that you were not alone in this world and that a mysterious guiding spirit watches over you with singular focus. You may have briefly glimpsed this strange spirit&mdash;or maybe you simply feel its presence in times of need.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl47_LabelType\">Once per day as a swift action, you can look to your guiding spirit for advice. The next time you roll a d20 in that same round, roll twice and pick the better result. If one of these two rolls is a natural 20, you can use this ability again that same day.</span></p>",
